_sText:
This map is a reworked version of aim_tg_dustland that lost kindly helped me with!  It's again made for the Tragedy Gaming clan's aim and cal rotation server that can be found here: 208.100.21.60:27015

I added a "construction" zone and a lot of decals, also a few props, i moved the tables onto the ground because they were slightly up.  Also, i fixed the leak in the other version of the map and optimized it slightly.
